    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wanted to <strong>see enemy soldier bodies fly into the stratosphere?</strong> Or <strong>jump 100ft high</strong> across enemy bases as you find the most creative ways to beat levels without being seen? Well, now you can! Flashbang enemies, shoot them into the horizon, throw enemy bodies virtually as far as you like, and explore the great many other tactics in this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game gives you the freedom to complete levels however you choose. Just want to have fun shooting enemies across the map? Great! Want to try your hardest to finish levels as fast as possible? Go for it! There is no &quot;right&quot; way to play this totally realistic first-person shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THROW/DRAG DEAD ENEMIES OVER THE HORIZON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/14cd59d1ffc6845c5eec3f4e6890ee20.poster.avif?t=1759022806\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/14cd59d1ffc6845c5eec3f4e6890ee20.webm?t=1759022806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/14cd59d1ffc6845c5eec3f4e6890ee20.mp4?t=1759022806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EARN YOUR HIGHEST SCORES TO UNLOCK ABILITIES, NEW LEVELS, AND MORE</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/e8618a38209e0b70c0101e758754acd0.poster.avif?t=1759022806\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/e8618a38209e0b70c0101e758754acd0.webm?t=1759022806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/e8618a38209e0b70c0101e758754acd0.mp4?t=1759022806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPERIENCE TOTALLY REALISTIC PHYSICS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/9f4a7fbf7b14015bde292d0dfa6a3828.poster.avif?t=1759022806\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/9f4a7fbf7b14015bde292d0dfa6a3828.webm?t=1759022806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078600/extras/9f4a7fbf7b14015bde292d0dfa6a3828.mp4?t=1759022806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>If you're interested, feel free to check out the <strong>Discord server</strong> for development updates and community discussions (you'll find the link in the panel on the right).</u></p>",
